{"tid":94231,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"港女使用ig 過程","createTime":"2017-01-25T05:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T16:56:12.000Z","uid":69486,"like":23,"dislike":212,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3438504644c99709311626eef4c69e32b076a8e2","tid":94231,"uid":69486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:18:54.000Z","msg":"1. 見到whatsapp有notification <br />\n2. unlock 部機，想check 下whatsapp <br />\n3.手指自己禁左入ig<br />\n4. 碌下ig story,順便即時自拍update<br />\n5. 碌下ig<br />\n6. 發現男神有update,但張相係同第條女一齊影<br />\n7. 嬲左<br />\n8. 冷靜番<br />\n9. 睇多次<br />\n10. 嬲右<br />\n(7-10 會重覆多次）<br />\n11. 又冷靜番<br />\n12. stalk 下條女ig<br />\n13. 發覺係private acc.<br />\n14. login 分身acc.<br />\n15. follow<br />\n16. request accepted<br />\n17. cap 低人哋ig 啲相，作為一陣同班姊妹小組討論嘅素材<br />\n18. 決定post 相向男神示威<br />\n19. 成個photo album 碌左n次，最後都係係求先醒左自拍嗰堆相入面揀其中一張<br />\n21. 過張相去修圖apps, 發覺張相影得塊面唔夠尖，決定重揀<br />\n22. 過第二張相去apps,發覺原來係同一張，決定照用<br />\n23. 選擇角色面形<br />\n24. 創建角色五官<br />\n25. 選擇角色身型<br />\n26. 較effect<br />\n27. reset<br />\n(23-27 重覆多次，視乎其自我外貌認知與真實外貌反差有幾大）<br />\n28. upload to ig,打番之前係fb page 見到嘅meme 做caption.<br />\n29. 有人係張相留言話自己串錯字<br />\n30. google translate完,發覺真係自己柒左<br />\n31. 改番個caption,del 番嗰留言<br />\n32. unfollow 嗰條友<br />\n33. 繼續碌<br />\n<br />\n有漏講聲，我補番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781d8ab4e1cdc0790a3f581130c7c61ed599d405","tid":94231,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"22aab41f1fcd4b0561289aad9b59237af7fa3e05","tid":94231,"uid":34456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:21:08.000Z","msg":"咁個wtsapp呢？"},{"pid":"732bc7ae644f9aab63ccc1fa67fb6ac55ceb6a5b","tid":94231,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"哈"},{"pid":"87665b50e64fbf7d3fa62280d97f54218f7d8d89","tid":94231,"uid":2032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T05:21:35